<FlowDocument xmlns="http://schemas.microsoft.com/winfx/2006/xaml/presentation"
              xmlns:local="clr-namespace:RFEM_Software.Help_Files.RBearHist_Help_Files"
              ColumnWidth="400" FontSize="14" FontFamily="Georgia">
    <Paragraph>
        This option allows the user to set the lengths of the x- and y-axes
and the location of the axes' origin on the printed page. All units
are inches.
The `Origin x-position' value is the distance from the left edge of the
page to the axes' origin.
The `Origin y-position' value is the distance from the bottom edge of the
page to the axes' origin.

    </Paragraph>
</FlowDocument>
